Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.67,0:00:40.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs95)\move(950,425,950,435)}政權交替啦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:40.00,Title,,0,0,0,,
